<html lang="ko">
	<head>
		<meta charset="utf-8" />
		<link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="/favicon.svg" />
		<link rel="icon" href="/favicon.ico" />
		<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width" />
		<meta
			name="description"
			content="Astro로 만든 개인 홈페이지입니다. About, Projects, Posts 페이지로 확장할 수 있는 첫 버전입니다."
		/>
		<meta name="generator" content={Astro.generator} />
		<title>개인 홈페이지</title>
	</head>
	<body>
		<header>
			<a class="site-name" href="/">Kei</a>
			<nav aria-label="주요 메뉴">
				<a href="/" aria-current="page">Home</a>
				<a href="/about/">About</a>
				<a href="/projects/">Projects</a>
				<a href="/posts/">Posts</a>
			</nav>
		</header>

		<main>
			<section class="hero" aria-labelledby="home-title">
				<p class="eyebrow">Personal Homepage</p>
				<h1 id="home-title">안녕하세요, 저는 Kei입니다.</h1>
				<p class="tagline">만드는 것과 배우는 것을 기록하는 개인 홈페이지입니다.</p>
				<p class="intro">
					이곳에는 앞으로 저를 소개하는 글, 진행한 프로젝트, 배운 내용을 정리한
					포스트를 차근차근 모아갈 예정입니다.
				</p>
			</section>

			<section class="next-sections" aria-label="앞으로 확장할 섹션">
				<a href="/about/">
					<span>About</span>
					<strong>나를 소개하는 공간</strong>
				</a>
				<a href="/projects/">
					<span>Projects</span>
					<strong>만든 것들을 모으는 공간</strong>
				</a>
				<a href="/posts/">
					<span>Posts</span>
					<strong>배운 것을 기록하는 공간</strong>
				</a>
			</section>
		</main>
	</body>
</html>

<style is:global>
	:root {
		color: #1f2937;
		background: #ffffff;
		font-family:
			"Apple SD Gothic Neo", "Noto Sans KR", Inter, ui-sans-serif, system-ui,
			-apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", sans-serif;
	}

	* {
		box-sizing: border-box;
	}

	body {
		min-height: 100vh;
		margin: 0;
		background: #ffffff;
	}

	header,
	main {
		width: min(100% - 40px, 1040px);
		margin: 0 auto;
	}

	header {
		display: flex;
		justify-content: space-between;
		gap: 24px;
		align-items: center;
		padding: 36px 0 20px;
	}

	.site-name {
		color: #111827;
		text-decoration: none;
		font-size: 1rem;
		font-weight: 800;
	}

	nav {
		display: flex;
		flex-wrap: wrap;
		gap: 18px;
		align-items: center;
	}

	nav a {
		color: #4b5563;
		text-decoration: none;
		font-size: 0.95rem;
		font-weight: 700;
		padding: 8px 0;
	}

	nav a[aria-current="page"] {
		color: #111827;
	}

	main {
		display: grid;
		gap: 72px;
		padding: 104px 0 96px;
	}

	.hero {
		max-width: 820px;
	}

	.eyebrow {
		margin: 0 0 16px;
		color: #2563eb;
		font-size: 0.82rem;
		font-weight: 800;
		letter-spacing: 0;
		text-transform: uppercase;
	}

	h1 {
		margin: 0;
		color: #111827;
		font-size: clamp(3rem, 7vw, 6.5rem);
		line-height: 1.04;
		letter-spacing: 0;
	}

	.tagline {
		max-width: 760px;
		margin: 28px 0 0;
		color: #111827;
		font-size: clamp(1.35rem, 2.4vw, 2rem);
		font-weight: 800;
		line-height: 1.45;
	}

	.intro {
		max-width: 680px;
		margin: 20px 0 0;
		color: #4b5563;
		font-size: 1.1rem;
		line-height: 1.8;
	}

	.next-sections {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: repeat(3, minmax(0, 1fr));
		gap: 18px;
	}

	.next-sections a {
		min-height: 148px;
		border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
		border-radius: 8px;
		color: #111827;
		text-decoration: none;
		padding: 24px;
	}

	.next-sections span {
		display: block;
		color: #2563eb;
		font-size: 0.92rem;
		font-weight: 800;
		margin-bottom: 28px;
	}

	.next-sections strong {
		display: block;
		font-size: 1.35rem;
		line-height: 1.45;
	}

	@media (max-width: 640px) {
		header,
		main {
			width: min(100% - 28px, 1040px);
		}

		header {
			align-items: flex-start;
			flex-direction: column;
		}

		main {
			gap: 48px;
			padding: 64px 0 72px;
		}

		.intro {
			font-size: 1rem;
		}

		.next-sections {
			grid-template-columns: 1fr;
		}
	}
</style>
